		   <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform2><span id=notbold>By:</span> <span id=>Anonymous</span></a><b><span id=></span></b>
		   <br><nobr><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Default [2.00]</nobr><br><br><img src="/shared/transp.gif" width="135" border="0" height="1"></td><td valign="top" class="mform2" width="100%"><p>Thanks for the information on Thorns and taunting!&nbsp;&nbsp;I just have one small clarification to make.  Draught of Fire is actually a *low* damage spell given to wizzie's so that they can have a less taunting DD that is still mana efficient.  I'll agree that this comparison speaks well for our DD power, but it's a slightly misleading comparison.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </p></td></td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="mform2"><table border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0 width="100%"><tr><td id=fs8></td><td align=right id=fs8 >0 Replies</td></tr></table></td></tr></table><tr><td>
